snippet.title: One Night at Flumpty's 3 (Developer Commentary, Kinda)
snippet.description:
Meant for those who have already experienced the game. I said I was going to make a postmortem instead of a developer commentary this time, but the video ended up being a bit of both, hence the "kinda".

On a technical note, I got a new microphone! Still getting used to it, but I like it.
